quran[9{c,v,t}:
6,102,"yeh hai Allah tumhara rab, koi khuda is ke siwa nahi hai, har cheez ka khaaliq, lehaza tum isi ki bandagi karo aur woh har cheez ka kafeel hai"
6,103,"nigehain is ko nahi pa sakteen aur woh nigahon ko pa laita hai, woh nihayat bareek been aur bakhabar hai"
6,104,"dekho, tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se baseerat ki roshniyan aa gayi hain, ab jo benaye se kaam le ga apna hi bhala kere ga aur jo andha banay ga khud nuqsaan uthaye ga, mein tum par koi Pasban nahi hon"
6,105,"iss terhan hum apni ayaat ko baar baar mukhtalif tareeqon se bayan karte hain aur is liye karte hain ke yeh log kahin tum kisi se parh aeye ho, aur jo log ilm rakhtay hain un par hum haqeeqat ko roshan kar den"
6,106,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! uss wahi ki pairwi kiye jao jo tum par tumahray rab ki taraf se nazil hui hai kyunkay uss aik rab ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai aur un mushriqeen ke peechay nah parro
6,107,agar Allah ki Mushiyat hoti to ( woh khud aisa bandobast karsaktha tha ke ) yeh log shirk nah karte tum ko hum ne un par Pasban muqarrar nahi kya hai aur nah tum un par hawala daar ho
6,108,"aur ( ae imaan laane walo! ) yeh log Allah ke siwa jin ko pkarte hain inhen gaaliyan nah do, kahin aisa nah ho ke yeh shirk se agay barh kar jahalat ki bana par Allah ko gaaliyan dainay lagen hum ne isi terhan har giroh ke liye is ke amal ko khushnuma bana diya hai phir inhen apne rab hi ki taraf palat kar aana hai, uss waqt woh unhen bta day ga ke woh kya karte rahay hain"
6,109,"yeh log kari kari kasmain kha kha kar kehte hain ke agar koi nishani hamaray samnay aa jaye to hum is par imaan le ayen ge ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke"" nishanain to Allah ke paas hain"" aur tumhe kaisay samjhaya jaye ke agar nishanain aa bhi jayen to yeh imaan laane walay nahi"
6,110,hum usi terhan un ke dilon aur nigahon ko phair rahay hain jis terhan yeh pehli martaba is par imaan nahi laaye thay hum inhen un ki sar kashi hi mein bhatakne ke liye chhorey dete hain
